<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 00:33:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着中东紧张局势接近白热化，美国稳步加大对红海胡塞武装的打击力度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/u-s-steadily-boosts-efforts-against-houthis-in-red-sea-as-middle-east-tensions-near-boil/0000018c-d162-ddba-abad-d3e3dcf10000</link><description>拜登政府因未能对胡塞武装的侵略做出足够的反应而受到一些前美国官员和国会议员的批评</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 22:27:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/u-s-steadily-boosts-efforts-against-houthis-in-red-sea-as-middle-east-tensions-near-boil/0000018c-d162-ddba-abad-d3e3dcf10000</guid></item><item><title>尽管哈马斯领导人被暗杀，以色列高级官员对人质协议谈判仍持“乐观”态度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/top-israeli-official-optimistic-about-hostage-deal-despite-hamas-leaders-killing/0000018c-d0db-daf6-a5df-d7ffe0b80000</link><description>这位资深消息人士还表示，以色列部长最近敦促巴勒斯坦人从加沙地带“自愿移民”的言论是“妄想”，以色列正在为国际法院的听证会做准备，并考虑向伊朗、南非和真主党请愿。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 20:34:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/top-israeli-official-optimistic-about-hostage-deal-despite-hamas-leaders-killing/0000018c-d0db-daf6-a5df-d7ffe0b80000</guid></item><item><title>被以色列拘留的加沙人数量一个月内猛增 150%；目击者：士兵在军事设施中虐待被拘留者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/number-of-gazans-detained-in-israel-jumps-150-witness-soldiers-abuse-detainees/0000018c-ca0b-d6c4-ab8d-ebbf60380000</link><description>661 名加沙人被拘留在以色列监狱中，此外还有数量不明的人被关押在斯德泰曼基地的军事设施中。一位熟悉那里情况的消息人士称，士兵正在殴打被拘留者，并将他们铐在栅栏上</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 19:36:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/number-of-gazans-detained-in-israel-jumps-150-witness-soldiers-abuse-detainees/0000018c-ca0b-d6c4-ab8d-ebbf60380000</guid></item><item><title>以色列男子因性侵犯被捕，据称使用了他通过宽松的枪支法规获得的枪支</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/man-arrested-for-sexual-assault-allegedly-used-gun-he-obtained-through-lax-regulations/0000018c-d09a-daf6-a5df-d7fe044b0000</link><description>自战争爆发以来，本·格维尔部制定的宽松规定已向约 30 万份枪支申请和 5 万份许可证发放。 《国土报》报道称，其中 14,000 个许可证是非法颁发的</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 19:17:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/man-arrested-for-sexual-assault-allegedly-used-gun-he-obtained-through-lax-regulations/0000018c-d09a-daf6-a5df-d7fe044b0000</guid></item><item><title>也门胡塞武装称他们瞄准了“开往以色列”的集装箱船，但没有损失报告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/yemens-houthis-say-they-targeted-israel-bound-container-ship-no-damage-reported/0000018c-cfe9-d4e1-ad8f-fff95e010000</link><description>法国航运公司达飞轮船告诉路透社，该船没有受伤，也没有发生任何事故。该公司还表示，这艘船的目的地是埃及，而不是以色列</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 18:08:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/yemens-houthis-say-they-targeted-israel-bound-container-ship-no-damage-reported/0000018c-cfe9-d4e1-ad8f-fff95e010000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯扣押的人质家属并不庆祝贝鲁特暗杀事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-03/ty-article/.highlight/families-of-hostages-held-by-hamas-arent-celebrating-the-beirut-assassination/0000018c-d057-daf6-a5df-d77f46660000</link><description>对于人质家属来说，哈马斯高级人物萨利赫·阿鲁里被杀绝非一张胜利的照片。虽然他们可能不会为他的去世而悲伤，但他们正在哀悼他被暗杀熄灭的希望之火</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 17:35:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-03/ty-article/.highlight/families-of-hostages-held-by-hamas-arent-celebrating-the-beirut-assassination/0000018c-d057-daf6-a5df-d77f46660000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家安全部长本-格维尔宣布将警察局长任期延长六个月</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/natl-security-minister-ben-gvir-announces-hell-extend-police-chiefs-term-by-six-months/0000018c-d054-daf6-a5df-d77c2c8f0000</link><description>这一消息是在科比·沙卜泰 (Kobi Shabtai) 警察局长任期即将结束前几周宣布的，并且符合政府紧急协议，即官员将继续留任直至战争结束</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 17:22:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/natl-security-minister-ben-gvir-announces-hell-extend-police-chiefs-term-by-six-months/0000018c-d054-daf6-a5df-d77c2c8f0000</guid></item><item><title>军方透露，以色列人质萨哈尔·巴鲁克在以色列国防军加沙救援行动中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/israeli-army-says-sahar-baruch-a-hostage-in-gaza-was-killed-during-rescue-operation/0000018c-d034-ddba-abad-d2b57e4d0000</link><description>这名 25 岁的以色列人于 10 月 7 日被绑架，上个月被宣布死亡。周三，军方表示他在一次营救行动中死亡，但许多细节仍不清楚</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 17:14:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/israeli-army-says-sahar-baruch-a-hostage-in-gaza-was-killed-during-rescue-operation/0000018c-d034-ddba-abad-d2b57e4d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡司法政变第二次打击：以色列最高法院推迟实施关键法律</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/second-blow-to-netanyahus-judicial-coup-top-court-delays-implementation-of-key-law/0000018c-d005-d4e1-ad8f-fcb511d20000</link><description>以色列议会三月份通过的所谓“丧失行为能力法”旨在阻止以色列总检察长宣布本杰明·内塔尼亚胡不适合担任公职，即使他违反了他签署的利益冲突协议，该协议禁止他参与司法系统的变革。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 16:33:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/second-blow-to-netanyahus-judicial-coup-top-court-delays-implementation-of-key-law/0000018c-d005-d4e1-ad8f-fcb511d20000</guid></item><item><title>自战争开始以来，有 1,600 名以色列士兵患有创伤后应激障碍 (PTSD)； 90人退役</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/1-600-israeli-soldiers-suffer-from-ptsd-since-start-of-war-90-discharged-from-service/0000018c-cfb7-d4e1-ad8f-ffb7ac230002</link><description>据以色列国防军称，大多数创伤后应激障碍病例都是经历过 10 月 7 日哈马斯大屠杀的士兵。以色列国防军心理健康部门担心预备役军人重返平民生活，表示担心“运作困难，日常生活开始变得毫无意义”</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 16:19:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/1-600-israeli-soldiers-suffer-from-ptsd-since-start-of-war-90-discharged-from-service/0000018c-cfb7-d4e1-ad8f-ffb7ac230002</guid></item><item><title>法国和德国谴责以色列部长将大批巴勒斯坦人迁出加沙的呼吁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/eu-countries-condemn-israeli-ministers-calls-to-move-masses-of-palestinians-out-of-gaza/0000018c-cfb7-d4e1-ad8f-ffb7c0100000</link><description>法国和德国对以色列部长斯莫特里奇和本格维尔的言论进行谴责，美国国务院也罕见地自发谴责</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 15:33:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/eu-countries-condemn-israeli-ministers-calls-to-move-masses-of-palestinians-out-of-gaza/0000018c-cfb7-d4e1-ad8f-ffb7c0100000</guid></item><item><title>欧盟高级外交官博雷尔表示世界必须强制解决以色列-加沙冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/top-eu-diplomat-borrell-says-world-must-impose-solution-to-israel-gaza-conflict/0000018c-cfc3-d266-a9bf-efc3eb5c0000</link><description>欧盟外交政策负责人何塞普·博雷尔强调了快速解决以色列和哈马斯之间冲突的重要性，并警告说“如果这场悲剧不尽快结束，整个中东可能会陷入战火”</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 15:04:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/top-eu-diplomat-borrell-says-world-must-impose-solution-to-israel-gaza-conflict/0000018c-cfc3-d266-a9bf-efc3eb5c0000</guid></item><item><title>最高法院裁决后，内塔尼亚胡的政党意识到司法改革已死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/following-top-courts-ruling-netanyahus-party-realizes-judicial-reform-is-dead/0000018c-cf6f-d4e1-ad8f-ffffa2da0000</link><description>利库德集团一致认为，无论从短期还是长期来看，推进司法改革都不再可能。该联盟将失败归咎于总理、司法部长亚里夫·莱文和议员西姆查·罗斯曼</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 14:56:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/following-top-courts-ruling-netanyahus-party-realizes-judicial-reform-is-dead/0000018c-cf6f-d4e1-ad8f-ffffa2da0000</guid></item><item><title>鲨鱼坦克：以加沙为试验场，以色列国防初创企业蓬勃发展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/suicide-drones-and-ai-with-gaza-as-testing-ground-israeli-defense-startups-flourish/0000018c-cf39-ddba-abad-cfb9a3ee0000</link><description>自杀式无人机和人工智能系统：严格的监管和主要国防公司的主导地位意味着以色列每年很少有小型国防初创公司成立。他们正在地缘政治紧张局势、军事预算增加和加沙战争中寻找新机遇</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 13:58:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/suicide-drones-and-ai-with-gaza-as-testing-ground-israeli-defense-startups-flourish/0000018c-cf39-ddba-abad-cfb9a3ee0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么黎巴嫩无法承受真主党和以色列之间的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/why-lebanon-cant-afford-a-war-between-hezbollah-and-israel/0000018c-cf7f-d4e1-ad8f-ffffa45f0000</link><description>黎巴嫩的经济因腐败和无能而受到重创，但最终趋于稳定，游客甚至开始回归。一场全面的战争将对黎巴嫩造成致命打击</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 13:37:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/why-lebanon-cant-afford-a-war-between-hezbollah-and-israel/0000018c-cf7f-d4e1-ad8f-ffffa45f0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯杀害歌手后，这首歌在以色列大受欢迎</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-song-became-a-big-hit-in-israel-after-hamas-killed-its-vocalist/0000018c-cf14-ddba-abad-cfb5db960000</link><description>“很遗憾我没有在她还活着的时候发行这首歌”：10 月 7 日，Ben Ronen 和 Tamar Samet 在 Nova 音乐节上，女歌手被哈马斯恐怖分子杀害后，这首精致而忧郁的歌曲获得了认可</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 13:18:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-song-became-a-big-hit-in-israel-after-hamas-killed-its-vocalist/0000018c-cf14-ddba-abad-cfb5db960000</guid></item><item><title>所有人的目光都集中在纳斯鲁拉身上，真主党领袖准备解决以色列杀害哈马斯官员的问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/all-eyes-on-nasrallah-as-hezbollah-chief-set-to-address-israel-attributed-killing/0000018c-cf20-d4e1-ad8f-ffb18dae0000</link><description>真主党周二表示，阿鲁里在贝鲁特被杀——普遍认为是以色列所为——不会不予答复。然而，一些人认为报复不会立即发生</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 12:34:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/all-eyes-on-nasrallah-as-hezbollah-chief-set-to-address-israel-attributed-killing/0000018c-cf20-d4e1-ad8f-ffb18dae0000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列也是我们的国家”：阿拉伯少数民族在加沙作战，同时面临国内不平等</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-is-our-country-too-the-arab-minority-serving-in-gaza-while-facing-inequality/0000018c-cb4c-d6c4-ab8d-ebfc204b0000</link><description>本周，自战争开始以来，第七名德鲁兹以色列国防军士兵在加沙被杀。在以色列最大的德鲁兹城镇达利亚特卡梅尔，当地人认同以色列，同时谴责其歧视性法律</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 11:44:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-is-our-country-too-the-arab-minority-serving-in-gaza-while-facing-inequality/0000018c-cb4c-d6c4-ab8d-ebfc204b0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯领导人被杀并不影响以色列在加沙的战争——但肯定会影响第二天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/al-arouri-killing-does-not-affect-the-war-in-gaza-but-certainly-the-day-after/0000018c-ce82-ddba-abad-cea30c3d0000</link><description>虽然在贝鲁特杀害哈马斯高级领导人是一次行动上的成功，但它对以色列加沙战争的影响却微乎其微。然而，它有可能加速哈马斯和法塔赫之间的和解，维护哈马斯的地位，并且更重要的是，保证其领导人的生存</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 11:38:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/al-arouri-killing-does-not-affect-the-war-in-gaza-but-certainly-the-day-after/0000018c-ce82-ddba-abad-cea30c3d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议员表示，每个人都清楚加沙人必须被摧毁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/its-clear-to-everyone-gazans-must-be-destroyed-israeli-lawmaker-says/0000018c-ce57-ddba-abad-cef736e40000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡党议员表示，“摧毁”加沙地带公民的广泛呼声证明右翼“一直”都是正确的</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 09:12:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/its-clear-to-everyone-gazans-must-be-destroyed-israeli-lawmaker-says/0000018c-ce57-ddba-abad-cef736e40000</guid></item></channel></rss>